{"tid":1198594,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【逃犯條例】譚小環小食店宣布周三全線罷市 老公戰勝肺癌熱住上街","createTime":"2019-06-10T09:31:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-10T14:11:34.000Z","uid":294,"like":100,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"ad6d7a23f5f880c4aac2e92e3df717a5f033f9a4","tid":1198594,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T09:31:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6OM3Byc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6OM3Byc.jpg&h=1b38610c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2370000/2372750/MESSAGE_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2370000%2F2372750%2FMESSAGE_600.jpg&h=9ba8a44f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今年46歲的香港小姐冠軍譚小環和老公莊強榮（Eric）結婚12年，感情要好，兩公婆拍住上搞小食店生意，大受市民歡迎，分店愈開愈多，不過兩年前Eric不幸證實患上一期肺癌，即時停工接受治療，令原來打算開6間分店的計畫都被迫擱置。幸好，老公接受治療後，情況已經好轉。昨日6月9日「逃犯條例．反修例遊行」，他都有參與其中，並帶同黃傘全程參與，似乎身體已經康復，實在戥兩人高興。<br />\n<br />\n遊行之後，小食店宣布周三停業一日。（圖片：渣哥一九九六FB)<br />\n<br />\n遊行完畢後，政府昨晚發表聲明指《條例草案》將於六月十二日在立法會恢復二讀辯論。由於政府沒有正面回應訴求，不少機構發起周三罷工罷市行動。"},{"pid":"6b03727a1f456550851d8b1370d867073770c073","tid":1198594,"uid":294,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T09:32:06.000Z","msg":"真香港小姐 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02d4c522d55a08f04136c517d26642ac66d1805a","tid":1198594,"uid":232082,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T09:32:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=LZecI195bvQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DLZecI195bvQ&d=AePTNAtL1N4PdcNq2S6jCJNY2w26zYPSLCKwhaLFqs8%3D&h=5a69c354\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=LZecI195bvQ</a><br />\n1:38 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=hor_